microservices.name: filemanage
microservices.options:
options:
  kind: Deployment
  containers:
  - build:
      args: {}
      dockerfileTemplateArgs: {}
      repo: https://code.aliyun.com/sreworks_public/mirror.git
      dockerfileTemplate: Dockerfile
      ciAccount: public
      ciToken: public
      repoPath: saas/upload/api/filemanage
      branch: master
    name: filemanage
  env:
  - DB_PORT
  - DB_HOST
  - DB_USER
  - DB_PASSWORD
  - DB_NAME
  - COOKIE_DOMAIN
  - APPMANAGER_PACKAGE_ENDPOINT_PROTOCOL
  - APPMANAGER_PACKAGE_ENDPOINT
  - APPMANAGER_PACKAGE_ACCESS_KEY
  - APPMANAGER_PACKAGE_SECRET_KEY
  - SREWORKS_FILE_PREFIX
  initContainers:
  - build:
      args: {}
      dockerfileTemplateArgs: {}
      repo: https://code.aliyun.com/sreworks_public/mirror.git
      dockerfileTemplate: Dockerfile-db-migration
      ciAccount: public
      ciToken: public
      repoPath: saas/upload/api/filemanage
      branch: master
    name: db-migration
